<!-- Purpose: To test the button element with the focus attribute. -->

<!-- Expected result: Clicking on the button should cause a Javascript alert dialog box to display -->

<title>XHTML Functional -- BUTTON - ONBLUR</title>

</head>

<body>

<form action="http://wetnap/cgi-bin/echo-form.cgi" method="post">

<p>When the mouse is clicked up over the button, a Javascript alert

dialog box will display with the following message: 'You have lost

focused (on Blur) on the link and as a result, this dialog box was

generated'.</p>



<p><button

onfocus="alert('You have lost on the the button (on Blur) and as a result, this dialog box was generated')">This is a button. Click on me</button></p>

</form>

</body>

